  "Description": "The TestChannelHandler goal is designed to test the functionality of a channel handler by utilizing caching to share state. It caches a value for 10 minutes, calls a function to handle test output on a specific channel, and verifies that the cached value matches the expected output. If the cached value does not match, it throws an error indicating the failure of the test.",
